LITB110.title: Beaver and Violet
LITB110.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 110 Beaver and Violet.m4v
LITB110.description: The Cleavers and the Rutherfords' picnic day turns into embarrassment for Beaver when a snapshot of Violet kissing him on the cheek appears on the cover of Ward's company magazine.

LISP24.title: His Majesty Smith
LISP24.path: ../Lost in Space/Lost In Space 24 - His Majesty Smith.m4v
LISP24.description: Doctor Smith delights that he is made ruler of an alien species until he learns that he is also their sacrifice.

STAN22.title: The Counter-Clock Incident
STAN22.path: ../Star Trek Animated Series/Star Trek Animated Series - 22 The Counter-Clock Incident.m4v
STAN22.description: The Enterprise finds itself trapped in a 'negative universe' which causes the crew to begin to grow younger and younger toward infancy.

SPRA44.title: Race the Laser Tank
SPRA44.path: ../Speed Racer/Speed Racer - 44 Race the Laser Tank.mp4
SPRA44.description: A gang of crooks have captured top-secret plans for a new weapon: a tank with a laser device. When Speed tries to interfere, they decide to test the tank on him.

LISP26.title: All That Glitters
LISP26.path: ../Lost in Space/Lost In Space 26 - All That Glitters.m4v
LISP26.description: Dr. Smith and Penny obtain a ring that will turn anything to platinum

LITB106.title: Ward's Baseball
LITB106.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 106 Ward's Baseball.m4v
LITB106.description: Larry Mondello convinces Beaver to play catch using Ward's valuable autographed baseball, with disastrous results.

LISP23.title: The Space Trader
LISP23.path: ../Lost in Space/Lost In Space 23 - The Space Trader.m4v
LISP23.description: After ruining the Robinson's food supply, Doctor Smith makes a deal with the space trader and gives his body for food provided he collects it in 200 years. The space trader comes to collect immediately.

LITB107.title: Beaver's Monkey
LITB107.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 107 Beaver's Monkey.m4v
LITB107.description: After June objects to his having a mouse as a pet, Beaver lets the mouse go into Metzger's field and answers an ad for a free pet monkey.

SPRA43.title: The Dangerous Witness
SPRA43.description: Speed is asked by the Chinese Princess Pedal to be her bodyguard, as a gang of assassins have taken a job on her.

SOKO22.title: Clash of the Giant Robot
SOKO22.description: The country of Melcon wants their own giant robot, and Giant Robot's birthday is spoiled by the news.

LITB108.title: Beaver Finds a Wallet
LITB108.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 108 Beaver Finds a Wallet.m4v
LITB108.description: Beaver and his friend Larry Mondello find a lost wallet stuffed with money, turn it in to the police station and hope that no one claims it so they can split the loot.

LISP25.title: The Space Croppers
LISP25.path: ../Lost in Space/Lost In Space 25 - The Space Croppers.m4v
LISP25.description: The Robinsons run into a group of space hillbillies whom Zachary believes might take him back to Earth.

TOPH1935.title: Top Hat
TOPH1935.description: A musical screwball comedy film in which Fred Astaire plays an American tap dancer who comes to London to star in a show produced by Horace Hardwick. He meets and attempts to impress Dale Tremont (Ginger Rogers) to win her affection.

LITB109.title: Mother's Day Composition
LITB109.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 109 Mother's Day Composition.m4v
LITB109.description: Beaver finds it a challenge to write a fifty word composition for a school assignment about his mother's life as a girl, especially when his classmates' mothers' lives seem much more exciting than June's.

POIR10.title: The Dream
POIR10.description: A famous pie manufacturer tells Poirot that he has dreamt of his own suicide, then dies under the same circumstances he dreamt about the very next day.

CSMS12.title: Encyclopaedia Galactica
CSMS12.description: Carl Sagan examines the possibility extraterrestrial life and discusses his skepticism about UFOs.

TOSM1948.title: The Treasure of the Sierra Madre
